item.title: Preview of Singapore Gifts Show 2015
item.description: The Singapore Gifts Show (SGS) 2015, held from July 8th to 10th at Suntec Singapore, presented a diverse selection of uniquely Singaporean gifts. A sample pack from organizer TTG Events included the NYP Postcard Set, SG50 Tattoos, Makan Buddies LEGO Minifig, Miniature Tea Book â€“ Volume II, and a Suction Mug. Makan Buddies LEGO Minifig (Graceland Gifts, Booth B21) These personalized LEGO figures demonstrate the potential for designing and 3D printing unique minifigures, as they are known by LEGO enthusiasts.
